freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Fatigue unresolved with sleep, mild chest pain, headache and a mild cough.

Had covid in November.  Vaccine 1 December.  Vaccine 2 January.  Left sided chest pain, cough, fatigue, new restrictive airway disease and arrhythmia, fatigue after vaccine 2.  Was about 95% precovid baseline before 2nd vaccine.  Resurfaced worse.

chest and lung pain, shortness of breath
